Title: Seeking the Dark
---
In the downward
spiral of love

You can do nothing
other than fall

and so come close
to us, becoming

who You are,
like a stone

thrown in a wide
arc into a deep

canyon, seeking the
dark where

all that is comes
alive in all

You are.
